          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>To configure the system to prevent the atm kernel module from being loaded, add the following line to the file  /etc/modprobe.d/atm.conf (or create atm.conf if it does not exist):

