          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify that the gssproxy package is not installed with the following command:

$ dnf list --installed gssproxy

Error: No matching Packages to list

If the "gssproxy" package is installed and is not documented with the information system security officer (ISSO) as an operational requirement, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Remove the gssproxy package with the following command:

$ sudo dnf remove gssproxy</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
