        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the owner of the directory "/var/log" to "root" by running the following command:

