        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>IP tunneling mechanisms can be used to bypass network filtering. If tunneling is required, it must be documented with the information system security officer (ISSO).</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>IA_Controls</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
