          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify that RHEL 9 has the openssh-server package installed with the following command:

$ dnf list --installed openssh-server

Example output:

openssh-server.x86_64          8.7p1-8.el9

If the "openssh-server" package is not installed, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The openssh-server package can be installed with the following command:
 
$ sudo dnf install openssh-server</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
