          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>RHEL 9 must not allow users to override SSH environment variables.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>SSH environment options potentially allow users to bypass access restriction in some configurations.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
