          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the GNOME desktop to not allow a user to change the setting that disables autorun on removable media.

Add the following line to "/etc/dconf/db/local.d/locks/00-security-settings-lock" to prevent user modification:

/org/gnome/desktop/media-handling/autorun-never

Then update the dconf system databases:

$ sudo dconf update</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
