        <STATUS>Open</STATUS>
        <FINDING_DETAILS>Tool: Nessus v10.10.0. Plugin feed: v202510220404. Scan policy: Policy Compliance Auditing
Time: 10/23/2025 03:18:11 PM
Result: FAILED

Policy Value: expect: ^[\s]*(?i)AutomaticLoginEnable[\s]*=[\s]*false[\s]*$
file: /etc/gdm/custom.conf
regex: ^[\s]*(?i)AutomaticLoginEnable[\s]*=[\s]*

Acutal Value: The following file(s) do not contain "^[\s]*(?i)AutomaticLoginEnable[\s]*=[\s]*": 
      /etc/gdm/custom.conf</FINDING_DETAILS>
        <COMMENTS />
