        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>If the rootpw, targetpw, or runaspw flags are defined and not disabled, by default the operating system will prompt the invoking user for the "root" user password.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
