          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure RHEL 9 to encrypt offloaded audit records via rsyslog by setting the following options in "/etc/rsyslog.conf" or "/etc/rsyslog.d/[customfile].conf":

$ActionSendStreamDriverMode 1</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
