          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify that RHEL 9 is configured to audit the execution of the "ssh-agent" command with the following command:

$ sudo auditctl -l | grep ssh-agent

-a always,exit -S all -F path=/usr/bin/ssh-agent -F perm=x -F auid&gt;=1000 -F auid!=-1 -F key=privileged-ssh

If the command does not return a line, or the line is commented out, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
